Manage NFSv4 export registrations

Usage:
  grainfs nfs export [command]

Available Commands:
  add         Register a bucket as an NFSv4 export
  list        List NFSv4 exports
  remove      Unregister an NFSv4 export
  update      Update an NFSv4 export

Flags:
  -h, --help   help for export

Global Flags:
      --endpoint string    admin Unix socket path (required, e.g. ./tmp/admin.sock)
      --log-level string   log level: debug, info, warn, error (default "info")
      --timeout duration   admin command timeout (e.g. 30s, 5m); unset = 30s default; 0 = uncapped (for long follow loops)

Use "grainfs nfs export [command] --help" for more information about a command.
